c: 8
v: 36
t: "Inene abo bangakholwayo, bade bachithe nobutyebi babo ukwenzela ukuthintela abantu bangangeni eNdleleni ka- Allâh, baza kuqhubeka ukwenza loo nto kodwa ekugqibeleni iza kuphethuka ibazisele imbandezelo phezu kwabo yaye futhi baza koyisakala. Abo bangakholwayo baza kuqundaniswa esiHogweni"